Localization.Name: Ship Showdown '52 Mercury Coin
Localization.Description: The Mercury Star Runner delivered a strong showing in the 2952 Ship Showdown with its second place finish. Ringed in blue, this coin commemorates the iconic courier ship with its image on one side and the Crusader Industries logo on the other.
